<div class="cb-section">
  <div class="cb-container">
    <h1>slack.com Integration</h1>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="cb-section">
  <div class="cb-container">
    <p>This add-on will connect your coworking space on Cobot with your <a href="http://slack.com">slack.com</a> account.</p>

    <p>New members on Cobot will automatically be invited to join your Slack team, so you donâ€™t have to add them manually.</p>

    <% if @spaces.any? %>
      <p>Select the space you want to add to Slack:</p>
      <ul>
        <% @spaces.each do |space| %>
          <li>
            <p class="f--clear">
              <%= link_to 'Manage Existing Teams', space, class: 'btn btn--blue btn--small f--right' %>
              <%= link_to space.name, [:new, space, :team] %>
            </p>
          </li>
        <% end %>
      </ul>
    <% else %>
      <p>Before you can set up Slack, you need to be the admin of a space on Cobot.</p>
    <% end %>
  </div>
</div>
